Extract the variables: Empirical auroral

flux_emp <- ncvar_get(nc[[1]], "flux")
energy_emp <- ncvar_get(nc[[1]], "energy")
mlat_emp <- ncvar_get(nc[[1]], "mlat")
mlt_emp <- ncvar_get(nc[[1]], "mlt")

Extract the variables: Satellite auroral

mlat_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "mlat")
mlt_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "mlt")
flux_n_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "flux_n")
flux_s_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "flux_s")
energy_n_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "energy_n")
energy_s_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "energy_s")
ut_n_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "ut_n")
ut_s_sate <- ncvar_get(nc[[2]], "ut_s")
